	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Have you soldered J5? About the jittering, try to keep the cables at a minimal length, especially the one going from pin 21 (video out). If you can't keep it short, maybe you can use a shielded cable?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


